";; appendix-02-debussy.slat
;; Book of Music — Appendix 2: Debussy and the New Harmony
;; Written 2026-07-13. Author: Lacuna Labs Engineering.
;; Real works: Claude Debussy (1862-1918)
;;   Clair de Lune (from Suite bergamasque, composed 1890, published 1905) — PD
;;   La Cathédrale engloutie (Preludes Book I, No. 10, published 1910) — PD
